{"tid":1963590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美死亡人數起越「珍珠港」與「911」   班農：應對中国政府進行紐倫堡式大審判","createTime":"2020-04-08T08:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T09:13:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aac3289de170da676efb8c981f8cead813af067b","tid":1963590,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T08:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.taiwandaily.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/0825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwandaily.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F0825.jpg&h=85cfc1d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐全球，美國近日已將疫情比擬為「珍珠港事變」與「911恐怖攻擊」，曾在川普政府任職的前白宮首席策士班農（Steve Bannon）表示，即使不涉及製作生化武器或實驗室外洩，就隱匿疫情和延後通報等罪責，應對中國政府進行紐倫堡式審判。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，美國感染武漢肺炎的死亡數如今已突破萬人，班農日前指出，台灣早在去年已向世衛組織警告，武漢肺炎會「人傳人」，WHO秘書長譚德塞也知情，1月14日竟還引述中國官方說法稱「不會人傳人」；對此，他呼籲，應全面調查病毒是否源自「武漢P4實驗室」。<br />\n<br />\n班農表示，國際法庭應該對中國官員如國家主席習近平、副主席王岐山等人，進行紐倫堡式的大審判，無論是否為人工武器，但有一個事實是，中國至少從去年12月開始就知道疫情，直到1月23日武漢封城前都在隱匿。<br />\n<br />\n據資料指出，「紐倫堡大審」（Nuremberg Trials）又稱「歐洲國際軍事法庭」 ，是盟軍於二戰結束後，在德國紐倫堡市舉行的國際軍事法庭審判，根據國際法和戰爭法對納粹德國進行起訴，有許多人在審判或執刑前輕生；在亞洲則有「東京大審」，正式名稱為「遠東國際軍事法庭（International Military Tribunal for the Far East）」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.taiwandaily.net/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%9A%B1%E5%8C%BF%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E7%8F%AD%E8%BE%B2%EF%BC%9A%E6%87%89%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C%E7%B4%90%E5%80%AB%E5%A0%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%AF%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwandaily.net%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%259A%25B1%25E5%258C%25BF%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585-%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25BE%25B2%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2587%2589%25E9%2580%25B2%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%25B4%2590%25E5%2580%25AB%25E5%25A0%25A1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AF%25A9%2F&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBYMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=9a5d8789\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.taiwandaily.net/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%9A%B1%E5%8C%BF%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E7%8F%AD%E8%BE%B2%EF%BC%9A%E6%87%89%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C%E7%B4%90%E5%80%AB%E5%A0%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%AF%A9/</a>"},{"pid":"dd5f0df4543ef349e4f9340cd09372d2a72d21d5","tid":1963590,"uid":152222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T08:47:26.000Z","msg":"fuck china<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420daa39e37a1c83a7d14de8262498cbea19cf3b","tid":1963590,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:03:16.000Z","msg":"制裁未呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d40ed6096910dc984ca59dd72b2428f210c084","tid":1963590,"uid":177339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:05:03.000Z","msg":"國師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />紐倫堡大審判"},{"pid":"088d18c172296df3be18f5560794df232b864732","tid":1963590,"uid":135661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:06:49.000Z","msg":"百國聯軍, 瓜分中國啦<br />\n香港就歸美國啦"},{"pid":"c4ddc985b06e2390edc3c8a5cbeb473ca593584c","tid":1963590,"uid":257622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:08:41.000Z","msg":"呢次係屌打支那嘅最好時機"},{"pid":"15fc6119c9355e1a22cee7a7541e5ffd8ff98f7f","tid":1963590,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:10:31.000Z","msg":"支持所有消滅支那既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292cd44ba321da26c68b9fa3285adade9da263b5","tid":1963590,"uid":28028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"張相咁撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}